Package src.java.documentReader

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DocumentReader
    A reader for the documents of a corpus, an implementation of this class has to be able to provide information that is processing.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultCorpusXMLHandler
    An abstract implementation of a DefaultHandler, adds complexity to this class by forcing the users that use this class to implement methods that are useful for processing the documents of the sample corpus.
    XMLDocumentHandler
    A derived class of DefaultCorpusXMLHandler
    XMLReader
    An implementation of a DocumentReader with the purpose of reading files in XML format.
